India Leaves Cap on FII Investment in Sovereign Debt Unchanged

-- B y   A n t o   A n t o n y
-- 
2011-09-15T09:01:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/india-leaves-cap-on-fii-investment-in-sovereign-debt-unchanged.html
India ’s government left a limit on
foreign institutional investment in the nation’s sovereign debt
unchanged, R. Gopalan, secretary in the Department of Economic
Affairs in the  finance ministry , told reporters in  New Delhi 
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
